Today is a special day for me, cough my birthday cough, and I want to show you something really special!
Have you ever wondered why some mega drives have EXT port at the backside?
It's for the mega drive modem! 🧐🤘
The older western mega drives have also a port for the modem, I guess it was planned and soon canceled because later revisions don't have one.
Swipe for some detail pictures of the modem and the minty box 😍
And yes I do have the instructions and so on but I can only post 10 pics 🤣
I even guess it was unused since I had to unpack the plastic film.
But I guess it's ok to unpack something today 🎂
Have you ever heard about the mega drive modem or even own one or used?

caption.text:
❔𝑬𝒎𝒊𝒍'𝒔 𝒔𝒕𝒐𝒓𝒚 𝒇𝒓𝒐𝒎: 𝑵𝒊𝒆𝑹❔
SPOILER ALERT.
Did you play NieR:Automata but didn't get to meet Emil before? His original story wasn't really mentioned, but if you knew him before you were visibly moved. 
Let's get to know him starting by the first Nier.
So, Emil was such a sweet and young boy, living into an old mansion. He had a strong power, after being experimented upon: everyone he looked at was turned to stone. He was terrified and kinda hated that power ofc, that's why he decided to wear a blindfold (as you can see from the picture).
He considered Nier and Kainé his older brother and sister....but he petrified Kainé trying to fight a monstrous Shade💔
Five years later he requested Nier to help him finding a cure. His sister Halua became the Ultimate Weapon, but Emil merged with her, gaining new powers and a skeleton body. He was able to see without harming the others tho, and managed to reverse the effects of Kainé's petrification. He was so ashamed of his new look, but his friends made him accept it, 'cause they loved him just the way he was.
Eventually, he helped Nier fighting the Shadowlord, but he lost control of his power and destroyed The Aerie. What really broke my heart, was his sacrifice: the last one. He wanted to save his friends and the others from Popola, at the Shadowlord's Castle. He didn't actually die, but he didn't have a body anymore, he was just a disembodied head rolling in the desert, trying to locate the others. 
You guys can imagine how much I love this character. He was so kind and pure, and he tried to do everything he could for his friends....💖
.
.
.
.
.

⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀ ⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀ ✭・.・✫・゜・⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀ ⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀𝗖𝗛𝗔𝗥𝗔𝗖𝗧𝗘𝗥 𝗗𝗘𝗦𝗖𝗥𝗜𝗣𝗧𝗜𝗢𝗡 ⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀❃𝗻𝗮𝗺𝗲 ~Katherine Matthews ⠀⠀⠀⠀❃𝗔𝗴𝗲 ~22 ⠀⠀⠀⠀❃𝗥𝗮𝗰𝗲 ~ human ⠀⠀⠀⠀❃𝗛𝗮𝗶𝗿 𝗰𝗼𝗹𝗼𝗿 ~ brown ⠀⠀⠀⠀❃𝗘𝘆𝗲 𝗰𝗼𝗹𝗼𝗿 ~ blue ⠀⠀⠀⠀❃𝗦𝗸𝗶𝗻 𝗰𝗼𝗹𝗼𝗿 ~ peach ⠀⠀⠀⠀❃𝗦𝗲𝘅𝘂𝗮𝗹𝗶𝘁𝘆 ~ bi ⠀⠀⠀⠀❃𝗚𝗮𝗺𝗲 ~ TEW 🤠👀 ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀ ⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀ ✭・.・✫・゜・⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀ ⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀⠀𝗪𝗥𝗜𝗧𝗜𝗡𝗚 𝗦𝗔𝗠𝗣𝗟𝗘 ⠀⠀⠀⠀ ⠀⠀ ⠀⠀⠀ Life couldn't get any better yeah right after the beacon hospital incident, her life went upside down.. "𝑴𝒖𝒔𝒊𝒄 𝒊𝒔 𝒋𝒖𝒔𝒕 𝒂𝒓𝒕 𝒕𝒉𝒂𝒕 𝒅𝒆𝒄𝒐𝒕𝒂𝒕𝒆𝒔 𝒕𝒊𝒎𝒆" -𝘛𝘸𝘰𝘚𝘦𝘵 𝘝𝘪𝘰𝘭𝘪𝘯🎵❤️
-
So far, orchestra has been everything I’ve ever wanted & thought it would be. I’ve been playing my viola for two years (although I haven’t been practicing as much as I should be for the skill level I want to be at) and finally joined a small community orchestra to dip my toes in the water. Everyone has been so nice and accepting 🥺🥺
.
I truly believe that music is the glue that unites every kind of person & it doesn’t matter 𝑤ℎ𝑎𝑡 you listen to because all music carries a message.
.
Anyways this is just a small step for now! I’ve learned to love classical music and am learning how to 𝐩𝐚𝐢𝐧𝐭 𝐢𝐧 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐚𝐢𝐫 with my instrument.
.
One day I’ll fulfill my dream of playing for a video game orchestra / cover orchestra! ❤️ But for now, this is where I am 🥰
